name: My GIFs
tagline: All my personal .gif files worth keeping
body:
### Welcome to the Money.
Here I've curated many of the finest gifs that the internet currently has to offer. 

```
$ have a look around
$ find some gifs you want
$ git checkout a branch OR
$ Download the .ZIP or tarball over there.
```

### Feel free to send a pull request to add new gifs. I don't know why anyone would ever do that, but if you feel inclined, go right ahead. I'll look at them. 

### Want a gif made? Let me know and I'll compose one for you. I know how to use Photoshop.

### Authors and Contributors
